message.content: The paper likely belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as it discusses the use of knowledge representation and reasoning in intelligent systems. Other likely sub-categories include "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as the paper focuses on natural language processing, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it contrasts KALM-QA with a machine learning approach, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the paper discusses question answering, and "cs.SE" (Software Engineering) as KALM-QA is a software system.
